    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuacamoleInsufficientCredentialsException, GuacamoleInvalidCredentialsException

    public class GuacamoleCredentialsException
extends org.glyptodon.guacamole.GuacamoleUnauthorizedException
    A security-related exception thrown when access is denied to a user because of a problem related to the provided credentials. Additional information describing the form of valid credentials is provided.
    Author:
    Michael Jumper
